# Mefi's NPC Buddy configuration file!
# January 2024 - mefistophiles Resident
# 
# This notecard allows you to define the default starting settings for your 
# NPC. Simply add this card to the contents of your NPC along with the NPC Buddy
# script and any animations you have defined.
#---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Configuration Guide: (You can remove all the lines starting with # if you prefer a 
#                                  shorter configuration file, these are for your reference)
#
#
# npcName - Defines the name of the NPC displayed in the titler.
# maxHealth - Defines the maximum health of the NPC.
# currentHealth - Defines the current health of the NPC
# titlerColor - Defines the color of the NPC's titler (using <R, G, B> SL formatting)
# isVisible - Defines if your NPC will be visible by default (1 or 0)
# textMode - Defines if you see text mode information at NPC start. (1 or 0)
# channelOn - Defines if your NPC will show it's communication channel in the titler.  (1 or 0)
#
# Animation Settings (For Animesh Only):
# dieAt0HP - Defines if your NPC will play the default Die animation (1 or 0, Animesh Only)
# standByDefault - Defines if your NPC will animate with it's standing animation (1 or 0, Animesh Only)
# animStandDesc - Allows you to override the "Stand" animation slot in the menu to something else.
# animStandName - Name for the default "Stand" animation.
# animFightDesc - Allows you to override the "Fight" animation slot in the menu to something else.
# animFightName - Name for the default "Fight" animation, 
# animDieDesc - Allows you to override the "Die" animation slot in the menu to something else.
# animDieName - Name for the default "Die" animation, 
#
#
#---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#
npcName Lost Soul Captain
maxHealth 400
currentHealth 400
titlerColor <1.0,0.0,0.0>
isVisible 1
textMode 0
channelOn 1
dieAt0HP 1
standByDefault 1
animStandDesc Stand
animStandName Stand
animFightDesc Fight
animFightName Fight
animDieDesc Die
animDieName Die
